+    """Extract a small, stable projection of visible AX state.
+
+    cua-driver's structured ``elements`` array intentionally excludes some
+    static text, while its markdown ``tree_markdown`` still contains display
+    values such as ``AXStaticText = \"42\"``. Preserve only those values (and
+    value-bearing text controls), never the full tree, so models can verify a
+    calculator/editor state without routing a screenshot through vision.
+    """
+    values: List[str] = []
